Draw an angled line to a given x coordinate.



```js
angledLineToX(data: AngledLineToData, sketch_group: SketchGroup, tag?: String) -> SketchGroup
```

### Examples

```js
startSketchOn('XY')
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> angledLineToX({ angle: 45, to: 10 }, %, "edge1")
  |> line([10, 10], %)
  |> line([0, 10], %)
  |> close(%, "edge2")
  |> extrude(10, %)
  |> fillet({ radius: 2, tags: ["edge1"] }, %)
```
